{"title":"First Memory","author":{"name":"Louise Glück"},"publishDate":"2011-09-01","lines":[{"line":"Long ago, I was wounded. I lived","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"to revenge myself","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"against my father, not","stanza":1,"number":3},{"line":"for what he was—","stanza":1,"number":4},{"line":"for what I was: from the beginning of time,","stanza":1,"number":5},{"line":"in childhood, I thought","stanza":1,"number":6},{"line":"that pain meant","stanza":1,"number":7},{"line":"I was not loved.","stanza":1,"number":8},{"line":"It meant I loved.","stanza":1,"number":9}]}